#: budgie-welcome:452
msgid "Open the menu and search for 'Install RELEASE'"
msgstr ""

#: budgie-welcome:504
msgid ""
"Seems that GNOME Software is not installed. If this problem persists even "
"after installing GNOME Software, please contact us with following error "
"message"
msgstr ""
"Kelihatan Perisian GNOME tidak dipasang. Jika masalah ini masih berlanjutan "
"selepas pemasngan Perisian GNOME, sila hubungi kami dengan menyertakan mesej"
" ralat berikut"

#: budgie-welcome:514
msgid ""
"Seems that App Center is not installed. If this problem persists even after "
"installing App Center, please contact us with following error message"
msgstr ""

#: budgie-welcome:763
msgid "Following tasks are in progress"
msgstr "Tugas berikut masih lagi berlangsung"

#: budgie-welcome:770 budgie-welcome:2003 budgie-welcome:2020
#: budgie-welcome:2048 budgie-welcome:2054 budgie-welcome:2568
msgid "Budgie Welcome"
msgstr "Aluan Budgie"

#: budgie-welcome:774
msgid "Budgie Desktop"
msgstr "Atas Meja Budgie"

#: budgie-welcome:902
msgid ""
"The following third-party repositories need to be added to complete the "
"installation:"
msgstr ""
"Repositori pihak-ketiga berikut perlu ditambah untuk selesaikan pemasangan:"

#: budgie-welcome:955 budgie-welcome:977
msgid ""
"Third-Party repositories and their packages are not supported by Ubuntu. You"
" should only continue if you trust the maintainers of these repositories."
msgstr ""
"Repositori Pihak-Ketiga dan pakej mereka tidak disokong oleh Ubuntu. Anda "
"hanya perlu teruskan jika anda percayai penyelenggara repositori tersebut."

#: budgie-welcome:958 budgie-welcome:980
msgid "Continue with the installation?"
msgstr "Teruskan pemasangan?"

#: budgie-welcome:964 budgie-welcome:986
msgid "Third-Party Repositories"
msgstr "Repositori Pihak-Ketiga"

#: budgie-welcome:975
msgid ""
"One or more packages need to be installed from a third-party repository that"
" you have previously added."
msgstr ""
"Satu atau lebih pakej perlu dipasang melalui repositori pihak-ketiga yang "
"anda sudah tambah sebelum ini."

#: budgie-welcome:1297
msgid "Welcome App"
msgstr "Apl Aluan"

#: budgie-welcome:1671
msgid "Could not gather data."
msgstr "Tidak dapat menghimpun data."

#: budgie-welcome:1751
msgid "GB"
msgstr "GB"

#: budgie-welcome:1752
msgid "GiB"
msgstr "GiB"

#: budgie-welcome:1753
msgid "MB"
msgstr "MB"

#: budgie-welcome:1754
msgid "MiB"
msgstr "MiB"

#: budgie-welcome:2005
msgid ""
"This snap is running on a distro that is unrecognized or on a development "
"release of Ubuntu that has not yet received its snap configuration.  Full "
"snap capabilities are unlikely to work."
msgstr ""
"Snap ini dijalankan dalam distro yang tidak dikenali atau masih keluaran "
"pembangunan Ubuntu yang belum mendapat konfigurasi snapnya. Keupayaan snap "
"lengkap berkemungkinan tidak berfungsi."

#: budgie-welcome:2022
msgid ""
"This snap is running on version of budgie desktop that is no longer "
"supported. Please upgrade to a supported version of the distro."
msgstr ""
"Snap ini berjalan dalam versi atas meja budgie yang tidak lagi disokong. "
"Sila tatar ke versi distro yang disokong."

#: budgie-welcome:2069
msgid "Status"
msgstr "Status"

#: budgie-welcome:2172
msgid " is in progress. Please wait for it to complete"
msgstr "masih dalam proses. Tunggu sebentar untuk menyelesaikannya"

#: budgie-welcome:2569
msgid "Find out about your operating system"
msgstr "Ketahui tentang sistem pengoperasian anda"

#: budgie-welcome:2571
msgid "Budgie Makeovers & Layouts"
msgstr ""

#: budgie-welcome:2572
msgid "Give the desktop a makeover with new themes, icons, fonts & layouts"
msgstr ""
"Berikan atas meja atau penampilan baharu dengan tema, ikon, fon & bentangan "
"serba baharu"

#: budgie-welcome:2574
msgid "Budgie Extras"
msgstr "Ekstra Budgie"

#: budgie-welcome:2575
msgid ""
"Customize the desktop with applets and mini-applications to provide extra "
"capabilities"
msgstr ""
"Suaikan atas meja dengan aplet-aplet dan aplikasi mini yang dapat "
"menyediakan keupayaan tambahan"

#: budgie-welcome:2578
msgid "Budgie Discourse"
msgstr "Budgie Discourse"

#: budgie-welcome:2579
msgid "Be part of the Ubuntu Budgie Community"
msgstr "Jadilah sebahagian daripada Komuniti Ubuntu Budgie"
